    <summary>Easy to use photo viewer with a clean interface</summary>
    <description> Available for free with no ads. One Photo Viewer is for those who don’t like the functionality of the Windows 10/11 default photo viewer. With a cleaner look and simpler functionality, it has many customization options and features such as slideshow, color adjustment, crop, resize, rotate, copy/paste clipboard, and more. All accessible by right click menu or keyboard shortcuts. It is also touchscreen compatible.

## Features

– Simple to use and customizable photo viewer
– Scroll through images with arrow keys or mouse buttons
– Select window border style Solid, Minimal or Auto hide
– Switch between black, white or transparent background
– Option to move and zoom entire window with mouse/touch
– Start a slideshow of images in a folder or drag-and-droped files

– Paste images from printscreen or other software
– Option to view toolbar and thumbnail panel (Pro)
– Crop, rotate, resize, adjust colors -> save or copy to clipboard
– View RAW formats, HEIC, WEBP (not guaranteed, see How To)
– View and convert to JPEG, PNG, TIFF or BMP
– Make GIF animation from loaded files

#### Microsoft Store app
One Photo Viewer is also available as [a Pro version with additional features in the MS Store](https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9NQC7CFDL54P).
 </description>
